\begin_inset Formula $x_{1}$
\end_inset

到
\begin_inset Formula $x_{1}+\Delta x_{1}$
\end_inset

这一小段钢丝绳受到的力有张力
\begin_inset Formula $-T(x_{1})$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $-T(x_{1}+\Delta x_{1})$
